---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Methodology — Knowledge That Compounds">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
      <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">KTC Methodology</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-warm-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Knowledge That Compounds
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The methodology behind the Brain Network. Five principles for building AI systems
        where knowledge persists, accumulates, and routes intelligently.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Insight -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-8">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mb-5"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">The core insight</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Standard AI tools treat every conversation as an isolated event. You ask a question,
          get an answer, and everything vanishes. The next time, you start from zero.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          But knowledge work doesn't function that way. Decisions build on previous decisions.
          Context matters. Institutional memory is what makes organizations effective.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          KTC is the methodology for building AI systems that work the way knowledge actually works:
          persistently, cumulatively, and intelligently routed to where it's needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Five Principles -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-warm-900">Five principles</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warm-900 text-warm-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-serif font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">Give AI Your Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
              AI must possess essential knowledge continuously, not just when asked. System prompts,
              persistent documents, and accumulated state form the foundation of every Brain.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warm-900 text-warm-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-serif font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">Capture As You Go</h3>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
              Knowledge should be externalized at the moment of creation, not retroactively.
              Every conversation, decision, and insight is captured in real time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warm-900 text-warm-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-serif font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">Build Living Systems</h3>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
              Systems that improve themselves through use. Every interaction refines the Brain's
              understanding, making it more effective over time without manual intervention.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warm-900 text-warm-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-serif font-bold">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">Distribute Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
              Multiple specialized Brains, coordinated by a central hub. Marketing knows marketing.
              Legal knows legal. And they share knowledge with each other when it matters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 flex gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warm-900 text-warm-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-serif font-bold">5</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2">You Stay in Control</h3>
            <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
              Human judgment is maintained at every step. AI assists but doesn't replace.
              Every decision point has a human in the loop, and you own all your data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="bg-warm-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-warm-50 mb-3">See the methodology in action</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-400 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          The Brain Network is KTC built into software. Start your free trial
          and experience compounding knowledge from day one.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
          <a href="https://app.gaudetteai.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-warm-50 text-warm-900 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-[15px] hover:bg-white transition-colors">
            Start Free Trial
          </a>
          <a href="/consulting" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 border border-warm-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-[15px] hover:text-warm-50 hover:border-warm-400 transition-colors">
            Custom Implementation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
